        --filter-19-86: invert(47%) sepia(70%) saturate(2%) hue-rotate(340deg) brightness(97%) contrast(84%)!important;
        --filter-20-86: invert(49%) sepia(19%) saturate(4%) hue-rotate(314deg) brightness(103%) contrast(91%)!important;
